Provenance
----------
All complaint records in `results.jsonl` are derived from publicly
posted pages on 800notes.com. No private, authenticated, or
login-gated content is included. No user was contacted, deceived,
or observed to produce this dataset.

Phone numbers are retained in E.164 form. Poster display names
appear only where the poster voluntarily chose a public display
name on 800notes.com. If you are a poster and wish your content
removed, contact the corresponding author listed in README.md.

